---
title: Almond & Chimichurri-Crusted Chicken with Zesty Roast Veggie Toss & Garlic Yoghurt
description: Sunset roasted veggies and chicken seasoned with chimichurri is a colourful combination of flavours. Dollop
over a cooling serve of garlic yoghurt to finish off the dish. At the end of the rainbow is a reward of almonds crusted
on top of the chicken to add a hint of nuttiness.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
